\id 2TI - Mbula 
\h 2 Timoti 
\toc3 2Tim 
\toc2 2 Timoti 
\toc1 2 Timoti 
\mt2 Ɓaria cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban 
\mt1 TIMOTI 
\imt1 Mǝncau 
\im Cautera mǝnia ka nda \bk Ɓaria Cauterǝa mala Bulǝs aban ká a ban Timoti.\bk* Gilǝî Timoti, muni aɓa paɓamuru a ban Kǝrǝsti lang nda aɓa kùrban a Roma a masǝlǝata túró male, tù nǝ lú male a pǝlǝa 67 ko 68 anzǝm ɓǝl Yesu. 
\ip Yì cauterǝa ka, kwarkiru na ace Timoti, kǝla muntulo mǝnana ɓimǝturo na sǝ gbasha male na ka. Kwarkiri ace ɓak ɓabumi ɓǝ̀ dum nǝ gandǝrǝu aɓa nutanni, sǝ ɓǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ túró mana yì Bulǝs pè ace Kǝrǝsti ka. Ɓǝ̀ bwal kanigir mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì mala Cau Amsǝban andǝ Kùrcau Mǝ'e, sǝ ɓǝ̀ pak túró male kǝla mǝkànìgìr andǝ mǝhama, ɓǝ̀ kǝa ɓanggi tanni ko ɓinǝcau nǝban aɓwana ɗàng, sǝama ɓǝ̀ ɓanggi kanigir nyir. À nunkiri arǝ agir ká-mǝɓane mala masǝlǝata apwari. 
\ip Aɓa mǝnia kat ka, à kasǝ ɓalǝ Timoti arǝ do andǝ tǝr pakkiagir mala ɓwa mana gilǝ mǝnia yì cauterǝa ka: paɓamuru male andǝ munyi, andǝ earcearǝu, andǝ gandǝrǝu, andǝ nutanni male aɓa kum patanni. 
\iot Agir mǝnana aɓalǝi ka 
\io1 Mǝncau\ior 1:1-2\ior* 
\io1 Ɓwangsǝban andǝ Ɓakɓabum\ior 1:3--2:13\ior* 
\io1 Kwarkiru andǝ nunkiru\ior 2:14--4:5\ior* 
\io1 Gìr mǝnana Bulǝs nda aɓalǝi ka\ior 4:6-18\ior* 
\io1 Masǝlǝatacau\ior 4:19-22\ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Makkun mala Bulǝs 
\p  
\v 1 Man yì cauterǝa ka, pur nǝ banam Bulǝs, mǝnana Ɓakuli nǝ nggearǝì twalam ɓǝ̀n duk mǝ'mishan mala Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka. Ɓakuli tasǝam ɓǝ̀n hamnǝ ce pàcau mala yilǝmu mǝnana sǝm ndanǝi aɓa kpapi ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka. 
\p  
\v 2 Mǝ nda ban gilǝì Timoti munem mǝnana ǝn earkiyi ace raka.\f + \fr 1:2 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 16:1\ft .\f* 
\p Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli Tárrû, andǝ Kǝrǝsti Yesu Mǝtala sǝm, lǝmdǝo ɓwamuru, ɓǝ̀ sǝn tǝ̀r mò, sǝ ɓǝ̀ cio wu kum dorǝpwala. 
\s1 Ɓakɓabum ace do nǝ mǝsǝcau 
\p  
\v 3 Du andǝ pwari ka, ǝn nggǝ ɗenyi nǝ we aɓalǝ ahiwi mem. Ən nggǝ pakki Ɓakuli yàwá, yì Ɓakuli mǝnana ǝn nggǝ kpate nǝ ɓabum mǝɓoarnsari, kǝla mǝnana akêm pàk ka.  
\v 4 Ɓǝ̀ ǝn ɗenyi nǝ mǝrǝm mǝnana a sukki a pwari gauwa ma'sǝm ngga, nzal sǝno kǝ pakkam. Ban nǝ̀ ɓoaram kǝ̀rkǝ́r, yi mǝnana ɓǝ̀ sǝm kum ɓamur rǝ sǝm a tarǝ sǝm ɗǝm ngga.  
\v 5 Ən nggǝ ɗenyi nǝ paɓamuru mò mǝɓafoe a ban Mǝtalabangŋo kǝla ulang pě mala keò mǝ'mɓwamae, yì Loyis andǝ nggo Yunis, sǝ ǝn sǝlǝna nǝma a ndarǝ lidǝmba aɓa mǝno yì paɓamuru ka nǝ rǝcandǝa.  
\v 6 Ace mani ka ǝn nggǝ kasǝ ɓālǝo ama, ɓoro mala Bangŋo mǝnana Ɓakuli po a pwari mǝnana ǝn tsǝk abuam a muro ka, lo tsǝì aɓa túró nǝ pi mala ɓabum.  
\v 7 Acemǝnana Bangŋo mana Ɓakuli pa sǝm ngga, mala ɓangciu na ɗang. Bangŋo mǝnana pa sǝm ngga, mala rǝcandǝa na andǝ earcearǝu andǝ bwalɓamuru.  
\v 8 Ace mani ka, ce kǝsǝkya pakko arǝ banggia aɓwana cau amur Mǝtalabangŋo ɗàng. Sǝ ce kǝsǝkya pakko arǝàm gbal ɗàng, kat andǝ amani ama mǝ nda a ndàkurban ace Kǝrǝsti ka. Nǝ rǝcandǝa mǝnana Ɓakuli po ka, dum nǝ kùr rǝǔ ace nutanni atàm ace hamnǝ Cau Amsǝban.  
\v 9 Ɓakuli amsǝ sǝm, sǝ tunǝ sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm duk aɓwana male amǝ fele.\f + \fr 1:9 \fqa sǝ tunǝ sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm dukdo tàr ɓamuru aceì. \ft Ko <<sǝ tunǝ sǝm ɓǝ̀ sǝm duk aɓwana male.>>\f* Pa ace atúró mǝnana sǝm pak ka ɗàng, nda àkǝ̀ ce male yì kani mana pusǝ sǝm ace ka, andǝ ɓwamuru male. Pà sǝm mǝnia yì ɓwamuru ka nǝ bu Kǝrǝsti Yesu sǝ yi kwakita ɓanza.\f + \fr 1:9 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Bit 1:3; Afi 2:5,8\ft .\f* 
\v 10 Sǝ ado ka, lǝmdǝna sǝmi bwāng nǝ yiu mala Kǝrǝsti Yesu, Mǝ'amsǝ sǝm, mǝnana ɓun rǝcandǝa mala lú, pǝlǝa lǝmdǝa sǝm njar mala yilǝmu mǝnana málá male pà kàm raka, aɓa Cau Amsǝban.  
\v 11 Sǝ Ɓakuli twalam ɓǝ̀n duk mǝ hamnǝ cau male, andǝ mǝ'mishan, andǝ mǝkànìgìr mala mǝnia yì Cau Amsǝban.\f + \fr 1:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Tim 2:7\ft .\f* 
\v 12 Nda gìr mǝnana tsǝa sǝ ǝn nggǝ nu tanni kǝla mǝno mǝ nda aɓalǝi ka. Sǝ mim ngga, kǝsǝkya kǝ pakkam arǝ mani ɗàng, acemǝnana ǝn súrǝ́nà rǝ ɓwa mǝnana ǝn gūlì arǝì, sǝ ǝn sǝlǝna ama gìr mǝnana ǝn nyingŋǝni wi a buì ka, nǝ̀ gandǝ bwale bà pwari nyare male. 
\p  
\v 13 Bwal kanigir mǝɓafoe mǝnana a kanì a banam ngga, ɓǝ̀ dupo gìrkànì mǝnana a nǝ kpate ka, sǝ pè aɓa paɓamuru andǝ earcearǝu mǝnana ndakam aɓa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka.  
\v 14 Tsǝk kiro arǝ cau mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì, mǝnana à po a buo, nǝ rǝcandǝa mala Bangŋo Mǝfele mǝnana do a ɓabum sǝm ngga. 
\p  
\v 15 Kǝla mǝnana a sǝlǝna ka, aɓwana mǝnana a bu-nzali Asiya ka, à pǝlǝna nzǝmia arǝàm kat à nyìngŋǝ̀nam. Ko nggearǝ Fijelus andǝ Hamojenis gbal ka, à nyìngŋǝ̀nam. 
\p  
\v 16 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli lǝmdǝì Onisǝforǝs andǝ amǝ ɓala male ɓwamuru, acemǝnana kǝ yiu a banam tùtù, sǝ kǝ ɓak ɓabumam, sǝ ko kǝsǝkya pakki wi arǝàm acemǝnana mǝ nda aɓa nsolo ka ɗàng.  
\v 17 Yiu male a Roma ka, altam kǝ̀rkǝ́r, gandǝa yi kumam.  
\v 18 Ɓǝ̀ Ɓakuli lǝmdǝì wi ɓwamuru ɓǝ̀ kum earmúrú a pwari nyare yiu mala Kǝrǝsti. Sǝ we ka a sǝlǝna rǝ ulang gbasha mǝnana pam a Afisu ka. 
\c 2  
\s1 Timoti ka mǝkpata Kǝrǝsti Yesu  //  na nǝ ɓabumi kat 
\p  
\v 1 Sǝ we munem, Timoti ka, dum nǝ mǝsǝkang-kangŋa aɓa ɓwamuru mǝnana sǝm ndanǝi aɓa dotarǝu ma'sǝm sǝnǝa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka.  
\v 2 Sǝ kanigir mǝnana a oê a kunam a ɓadǝmbǝ amǝ'nakún pas ka, twali, kànî aɓwana amǝ'mǝsǝcau nì mǝnana à nǝ̀ gandǝ tasǝi aban ká a ban aɓea aɓwana gbal ka.  
\v 3 Dum nǝ gandǝrǝu aɓa tanni atàm kǝla soje mǝɓoarne mala Kǝrǝsti Yesu.  
\v 4 Kǝ soje pâ kàm mǝnana nǝ̀ oasǝ ɓamúrì aɓa dukiado mala aɓwana mǝnana asoje na raka ɗàng, acemǝnana kǝ earce nǝ̀ pwasǝbum ɓwa mǝnana twali a soje ka.  
\v 5 Anggo gbal, ɓwa mǝnana nda aɓalǝ amǝ kārǝki amire ka, kǝ li ɗàng, she ɓǝ̀ ɓangŋǝna mire masǝlǝna tè pepè, kpana atà nggurcau mǝnana à tsǝki amǝ mire ka.  
\v 6 Mǝrya mana pak túró mǝcandǝe ka, ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ li tadǝmba ɓǝla agirɓaban mǝno tanniki aɓalǝi ka.  
\v 7 Pak ɗenyicau amur agir mǝnana ǝn nggǝ banggo ka. Ɓakuli ka, nǝ̀ mǝngio ɓalǝ amǝnia yì agir ka kat, ace mǝnana wu bwaltea. 
\p  
\v 8 Koya pwari ka, dum nǝ ɗenyicau ama, Yesu Kǝrǝsti, Mǝkà Dauda ka, à loasǝi a ɓembe. Mǝnia ka nda Cau Amsǝban mana ǝn nggǝ hamnǝi ka.  
\v 9 Sǝ acemǝnana ǝn nggǝ hamnǝ mǝnia yì Cau Amsǝban ngga, mǝ ndya ǝn nggǝ tanni, à kùrram nǝ ansolo kǝla ɓwa mǝnana mǝɓealɓikea na ka. Sǝa ma cau mala Ɓakuli ka, à kùrrì ɗàng.  
\v 10 Ace mani ka, ǝn earǝna mǝ dum nǝ gandǝrǝu aɓa ko man, ace aɓwana mana Ɓakuli tària ka, ace mǝnana yia gbal ka ɓǝà kum amsǝban mana aɓa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka, atārǝia andǝ gulo mǝnana pà nǝ̀ mal raka.  
\v 11 Mǝnia yì cau ka, cau na à nǝ̀ earnǝi, mana ama: 
\q1 <<Ɓǝ̀ sǝm wu sǝnǝi ka, 
\q2 sǝm nǝ̀ dum nǝ 
\q2 yilǝmu sǝnǝi gbal. 
\q1  
\v 12 Ɓǝ̀ sǝm twal 
\q2 gandǝrǝu aɓa tanni ka, 
\q2 sǝm nǝ̀ duk amurǝma atè. 
\q1 Ɓǝ̀ sǝm tǝmce súrǝè ka, 
\q2 yì gbal ka, 
\q2 nǝ̀ tǝmce súrǝ̀ sǝm.\f + \fr 2:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Mat 10:33; Luk 12:9\ft .\f* 
\q1  
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ sǝm dum nǝ 
\q2 mǝsǝcau raka, 
\q1 yì ka, dumǝna nǝ mǝsǝcau, 
\q2 acemǝnana pà nǝ̀ tǝmce 
\q1 ɓamúrì ɗàng.>> 
\s1 Mǝtúró mǝnana Ɓakuli earnǝi ka 
\p  
\v 14 Wu kǝ kasǝ ɓalǝ aɓwana arǝ amǝnia yì agir ka, sǝ wu nunkiria a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli, ɓǝà ɗeki makgìr amur acau. Amǝno yì amakgìr ka, à pànǝ ɓoaro ɗang, à nǝ̀ kiɗiki aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ okia ace ka.  
\v 15 Ɓariki nǝ pa rǝcandǝa arǝ túró kàngkàng, ace mǝnana wu lǝmdǝ rǝò a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ earnǝ we. Duk mǝtúró mǝɓoarne, mǝnana kǝsǝkya pa nǝ̀ pakki wi arǝ túrè raka, mǝtúró mǝnana kǝ mǝngi ɓá cau mǝ'mǝsǝcau nì pepè ka.  
\v 16 Tārǝto arǝ naki acauɓana andǝ amǝnana à pà nǝ̀ yinǝì Ɓakuli gulo raka, acau ɓanggea mǝnana à kǝ tasǝta aɓwana nǝ tasǝa aɓa ɗwanyi súrǝ̀ Ɓakuli ka.  
\v 17 Akanìgìr ulang mǝno ka à kǝ akiban kǝla barya mpenye-gula mǝnana kǝ li ɓa'nyam ɓwa ka. Aburana ɓari mǝnana à yì kania aɓwana ulang amǝno yì akanìgìr ka, à nda ka, Hemǝniyos andǝ Filetus.  
\v 18 À ɗekini njar mala mǝsǝcau, à kǝ na ama loapi ɓembe mala alú kutina. Nǝ ulang mǝnia yì kanigir ka, à tsǝ̀ngŋǝ̀nà aɓwana pas à ɗekina paɓamuru malea a ban Ɓakuli.  
\v 19 Kat andǝ amani ka, mǝsǝcau mala Ɓakuli ka, camǝna kàngkàng kǝla kusǝɓa mǝnana à kwaki sǝ pà nǝ̀ dǝurǝ raka. Amurí ka à nyoulǝ mǝnia yì cau ka ama: <<Mǝtalabangŋo súrǝ́nà rǝ aɓwana mǝnana à nda ka male ka,>> sǝ <<Koya ɓwa mǝnana kat kǝ na ama mala Mǝtalabangŋo na ka, dumǝna púp nǝ̀ gapita rǝia andǝ ɓealɓikea.>> 
\p  
\v 20 Aɓa ɓala mǝgule ka, agirtúró ndakam ɗàngɗáng; aɓea ka, à pea nǝ bolo-njengǝlan andǝ bolo-azǝrfa, sǝ aɓea ka, à pea nǝ nggun andǝ dǝɓang. Amǝnana boalea gul ka, à nda ace pwari lamsan mǝɓoarne, sǝ amana boalea gul raka, à nda ace túró ɓala mala koya pwari ka.  
\v 21 Ɓǝ̀ ɓwa lak ɓamúrì aɓalǝ amǝno yì aɓealu mǝɓane, do aɓa ɓoarnsari ka, nǝ̀ duk girtúró ace túró mǝgule, mǝnana à tàrni ndanǝ ɓoaro a ban mǝtala-ɓala, sǝ à gilǝkini ace koya túró mǝɓoarne ka.  
\v 22 Ɓanggi koya suno mala lo-ɓwa, sǝ wu ɓangŋa atà ɓealɓoarna, andǝ paɓamuru, andǝ earcearǝu, andǝ do rǝpwala, atarǝ wun wunǝ aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ pak hiwi a ban Mǝtalabangŋo nǝ ɓabum mǝɓoarnsari ka.  
\v 23 Kǝa kánǝ ɓamur rǝo aɓalǝ agǝmi makgìr andǝ amana sǝlǝe pà aɓalǝia raka ɗàng, acemǝnana we ka a sǝlǝna ama, mǝno ka kǝ yinǝ munǝo.  
\v 24 Sǝ guro mala Ɓakuli ka, ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ kúni ɓua aban loàsǝ̀ban andǝ kǝɓwa ɗàng. Ɓoaro ɓǝ̀ duk ɓukɓuk nǝ aɓwana kat. Ɓǝ̀ duk mǝ'sǝlǝ kanigir andǝ ɓwa nǝ munyi.  
\v 25 Aɓa pê ɓukɓuk ka, kwarkir aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ ɓinǝ earnǝ mǝsǝcau ka. Yakǝla ka, Ɓakuli nǝ̀ nggaɗi ɓabumia, sǝ à nǝ̀ vwaki buia arǝ cauɓikea à nǝ̀ pwanzali, ɓǝ̀ kyan nǝia aɓa súrǝ̀ mǝsǝcau.  
\v 26 Aɓa mǝno anggo ka, à nǝ̀ nyare aɓa ɗenyicau malea, à nǝ̀ purî ɓá gbǝ́lî mala Shetan mǝnana bwalia guro, sǝ cia à kǝ kpata cau male ka. 
\c 3  
\s1 Ɓike mala ado a masǝlǝata apwari 
\p  
\v 1 We ka, sǝlǝ ama, kwano mala ado nǝ̀ nggá yiu a masǝlǝata apwari.  
\v 2 Ɓwapǝndǝa nǝ̀ duk amǝ earce ɓamuria, amǝ rufi atà boalo, amǝ nggori andǝ amǝ twàlɓamúrû. À nǝ̀ duk amǝ ɓǝsǝki Ɓakuli, andǝ amǝ mgbikiru a ban atárrià andǝ anggea, andǝ amǝ ɗwanyi pak yàwá, à pà nǝ̀ fali nǝ Ɓakuli ɗang.  
\v 3 Ɓwapǝndǝa nǝ̀ dum nǝ ɗwanyi earcearǝu, à nǝ̀ duk amǝ ɗwanyi twalbani, amǝ twalki alullǝ aɓwana, amǝ ɗwanyi bwalrǝu, amǝ bum tǝra, à pà nǝ̀ earce gìr mǝɓoarne ɗàng.  
\v 4 Ɓwapǝndǝa nǝ̀ duk amǝ mak aɓea, amǝ ɗwanyi tsǝkiru, amǝ gusǝlǝ-múrû, andǝ amǝ earce banɓoarnado amur earce Ɓakuli.  
\v 5 À nǝ̀ lǝmdǝí a nza kǝla yià ka aɓwana mala Ɓakuli na, sǝ à ɓinǝ pà ɓamuria arǝ rǝcandǝa mala Ɓakuli mǝnana nǝ̀ cia à nǝ̀ duk do mala amǝkwaɗi ka. A ulang amǝnia yì aɓwana ka, wu ɓanggi bania. 
\p  
\v 6 À nda ka aɓwana mǝnana à kǝ swár zàng, à kǝ kutiki arǝ aɓala mala aɓwana, à kǝ swár amamǝna amǝ'ɗwanyi sǝlǝe, mǝnana cauɓikea akina ɓabumia, sǝ à kǝ ɓangŋa atà koya ulang suno mǝɓane ka.  
\v 7 A ulang amamǝna mǝno ka, à kǝ kyale atà akanìgìr ɗàngɗáng koya pwari, sǝ ko à kǝ gandǝ bwalta mǝsǝcau ɗàng.  
\v 8 Kǝla mǝnana Janis andǝ Jambǝris ɓinǝì Musa à earnǝi raka, anggo sǝ aman yì aɓwana ka, à ginǝki mǝsǝcau. Yia ka, aɓwana na mǝnana ɓabumia sharna aɓa cauɓikea, sǝ paɓamuru malea ka, mǝɓafoe na ɗang.\f + \fr 3:8 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Pur 7:11\ft .\f* 
\v 9 Sǝa ama yia ka, à pà nǝ̀ ká ɗār ɗang; ɗwanyi sǝlǝe malea nǝ̀ lǝmdǝ rǝì a ban aɓwana kat, kǝla mǝnana kum a Janis andǝ Jambǝris ka. 
\s1 Masǝlǝata kwarkiru mala  //  Bulǝs a ban Timoti 
\p  
\v 10 Sǝ we Timoti ka, a súrǝ́nà rǝ kanigir mem andǝ ɓealam. A súrǝ́nà rǝ kanì mala ɓabumam aɓa do mem. A súrǝ̀ paɓamuru mem, andǝ munyi, andǝ earcearǝu, andǝ gandǝrǝu mem;  
\v 11 kat andǝ atanni mem, andǝ apatanni mana à yiu amuram ngga. A súrǝ́nà rǝ kanggǝrang tanni mǝnana à pam a Antiyok, andǝ Ikoniya andǝ Listǝra ka. Kat andǝ amani ka, Mǝtalabangŋo amsǝam aɓalǝ amǝnia yì agir ka kat.\f + \fr 3:11 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 13:14-52; 14:1-20\ft .\f* 
\v 12 E, sǝ koya ɓwa na ear ama nǝ̀ duk do ɓealɓoarna aɓa Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka, à nǝ̀ pè wi tanni.  
\v 13 Sǝ amǝ'ɓealɓikea andǝ amǝ'swarkiban ngga, à nǝ̀ lidǝmba nǝ ɓealɓikea aban ká kìɗìkì, à nǝ̀ nggǝ swarki aɓwana sǝ yià gbal ka à nǝ̀ nggǝ swarkia.  
\v 14 Sǝ we ka, lidǝmba aɓa mǝsǝcau mǝnana à kàniô, sǝ a earnǝi ka, acemǝnana a súrǝ́nà rǝ aɓwana mǝnana à kàniô gìr ka.  
\v 15 Sǝ ɓǝ̀ ɓālǝo kasǝ ama, lo mô a muntulo ka, a súrǝ̀ a Malǝmce mǝfele mana à gandǝ po sǝlǝe ace kum àwá nǝ paɓamuru a ban Kǝrǝsti Yesu ka.  
\v 16 Malǝmce mǝfele kat ka, ǝn'yali mala Ɓakuli na, sǝ ndanǝ ɓoaro ace kànì mǝsǝcau, andǝ lǝmdǝ ɓwarkio, andǝ gilǝkiban aɓa ɓwarkio, andǝ kwarkiru ace pàk mǝɓoarne.  
\v 17 Ɓakuli kǝ pangŋǝ̀nà túró nǝi, ace gilǝki aɓwana male, ɓǝà dum nǝ kùr rǝǔ ace pàk koya gìr mǝɓoarne. 
\c 4  
\s1 À kwarkir Timoti ɓǝ̀ tamsǝ kusǝì  //  ace lidǝmba mala túró  //  mala Ɓakuli 
\p  
\v 1 Ən nggǝ nunkiro a ɓadǝm Ɓakuli andǝ Kǝrǝsti Yesu, mǝnana nǝ̀ yia ɓashì aɓwana mǝnana à ndanǝ yilǝmu andǝ amǝnana à wuna ka, a pwari yiu male mǝnana nǝ̀ yiu a dumsǝ domurǝm male ka.  
\v 2 We ka, hamnǝ cau mala Ɓakuli. Do aɓa gilǝrǝu ace mǝnia yì túró ka, ko njar nda kam ko pà kàm ɗàng. Lǝmdǝì aɓwana ɓwarkio malea, nunkiria, sǝ wu ɓak ɓabumia nǝ munyi mǝgule andǝ kwarkiru ɓukɓuk.  
\v 3 Acemǝnana pwari nda kǝ yiu ka, mǝnana ɓwapǝndǝa pa nǝ̀ earnǝ kanigir mǝɓoarne raka. A kun mani ka, à nǝ̀ ramba amǝkànìgìr a rǝia, mǝnana à nǝ̀ pwasǝbumia nǝ nea wia gìr mǝnana kiria kǝ oākia arǝì, sǝ à earkiyi ce oe ka.  
\v 4 À nǝ̀ ɓinǝ mǝsǝcau, à pànǝ earce oe ɗang, à nǝ̀ o atà njarnzǝne.  
\v 5 Sǝ we ka, hami rǝo aɓa koya ulang ɓealu mala do, dumnǝ gandǝrǝu aɓa nutanni, pak túró mala Mǝhama, lùmsǝ túró mǝnana a pakkiyi ace Ɓakuli ka.  
\v 6 Ma mem ngga, pwari kārǝ́na ɓǝ̀ ǝn pa yilǝmem kǝla ɓoro mǝnana a pè Ɓakuli ka. Pwari nying ɓanza mem kārǝ́na.  
\v 7 Ən munǝna munǝo mǝɓoarne, mire mem bwalǝna masǝlǝate, sǝ ǝn camǝna kàngkàng aɓa paɓamuru arǝ Kǝrǝsti māna à pam a buam ngga.  
\v 8 Sǝ ado ka, tangnakusǝam, yì jeko mala túró-cauɓoarna ka, nda rǝ kundǝam, mǝnana Mǝtalabangŋo, Mǝɓashi aɓa mǝsǝcau nǝ̀ pam a Pwari nyare male ka. Sǝ tangnakusǝu man ngga pa acem nǝmurǝam ɗàng, nda gbal acea aɓwana mǝnana kat à kǝ earce yiu male ka. 
\s1 Masǝlǝata cau mala Bulǝs 
\p  
\v 9 Timoti, ɓariki, yiu a banam a kaurǝa.  
\v 10 Acemǝnana Dimas ɗeki nam, ace earce mǝnia yì ɓanza ka, umǝna a Tasalonika. Sǝ Kǝrǝsen ngga, umǝna a Galati, sǝ mala Titus ka, umǝna a Dalmatiya.\f + \fr 4:10-11\ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Kol 4:10-14; Film 24; 2Kor 8:23; Gal 2:3; Tit 1:4; Atúró 12:12,25; 13:13; 15:37-39\ft .\f* 
\v 11 Kǝ Luka, nda mǝnana a banam ngga. Ɓǝ̀ a nǝ yiu ka, wu yiu wunǝ Markus, acemǝnana nǝ̀ yia bwalàm nggàm arǝ túró mem.  
\v 12 Tikikus ka, ǝn turni a Afisu.\f + \fr 4:12 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 20:4; Afi 6:21,22; Kol 4:7,8\ft .\f* 
\v 13 Ɓǝ̀ a nǝ yiu ka, yinǝàm nǝ nggea-daura mǝnana ǝn nyi a Tǝros, a ɓala mala Karpus ka. Sǝ wu yinǝàm nǝ amalǝmce mem, andǝ anggu mǝnana à nǝ̀ gilǝ gir aɓalǝia ka.\f + \fr 4:13 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 20:6\ft .\f* 
\v 14 Alizanda mǝ'ntùl, pakkam gìr mǝɓike\f + \fr 4:14 \fq pakkam gìr mǝɓike: \ft Ko <<kìɗikiàm agir>>\f* kǝ̀rkǝ́r. Ɓakuli nǝ̀ ɓashi wi ace agir mǝnana pàk ka.\f + \fr 4:14 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt 1Tim 1:20; Ang 62:12; Rom 2:6\ft .\f* 
\v 15 We gbal ka, tsǝk kiro arǝì, acemǝnana kǝ munǝ arǝ koya cau sǝm bang ngga. 
\p  
\v 16 Tita ká mem a ɓadǝm mǝ'ɓashi ka, kǝɓwa cam a nzǝmam ɗàng. Aɓwana mesǝe, à nyem nǝmurǝam. Ɓakuli ɓǝ̀ twalia wia banì, ɓǝ̀ kǝa ɓashia wia ɗàng.  
\v 17 Sǝama Mǝtalabangŋo nda atàm sǝ pam rǝcandǝa ace mǝnana ɓǝ̀ ǝn hamnǝ Cau Amsǝban kat ace aɓwana mana amǝ Yahudi na raka ɓǝà oè. Nyar ɗǝm ngga, amsǝam a bu lú, a kún a'im mǝnana ɓǝ́ à nǝ̀ túrǎm aɓalǝia ka.  
\v 18 Yì, Mǝtalabangŋo ka, nǝ̀ amsǝam aɓalǝ aɓealɓikea kat, sǝ nǝ̀ kánǝ mim jam aɓa domurǝm male mala kùli. Gulo ka, male na kat, masǝlǝate pà kàm ɗàng. Ɓǝ̀ do anggo. 
\s1 Masǝlǝata makkun mala Bulǝs 
\p  
\v 19 Makkia Pǝrisǝla andǝ Akila kûn, andǝ amǝɓala mala Onisǝforǝs.\f + \fr 4:19 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 18:2; 2Tim 1:16,17\ft .\f* 
\v 20 Arasǝtus ka, nda più a Korinti, sǝ Tǝrofimus ka, ǝn nyi nǝ rǝkwana a Miletus.\f + \fr 4:20 \ft Ɓalli gbal aɓa: \xt Atúró 19:22; Rom 16:23; Atúró 20:4; 21:29\ft .\f* 
\p  
\v 21 Ɓariki, yiu sǝ ɓǝ̀ kunɗwal sulǝo. Yubulǝs kǝ makko kûn, sǝ anggo gbal Pudem, andǝ Linos, andǝ Kǝlaudiya, andǝ acilia amǝ'eamrǝarǝu kat. 
\p  
\v 22 Ɓǝ̀ Mǝtalabangŋo do atà bangŋo mò. Ɓǝ̀ ɓwamuru male do atà wun kat.